channel.title: About the Best Practices category
channel.description: Use the Best Practices category to discuss the latest and greatest ideas in what we can do to make kids more mobile and safer. Topics may include seating, harnesses, safety, fundraising, release forms, etc. Included all the things you do, or plan to do to make GoBabyGo even better.
